  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126700/extras/645a76edc80755d57ed04a02fd1ee5ea.avif?t=1684485234\" width=576 height=64 /></span><br>Meet Olivia and Elodie, two sisters on an adventure in an infinite imaginary landscape. Can you help them work together in order to discover what secrets are in store?<br><br>Elodie is tasked with collecting food and luring out animals while Olivia guides animals to farms. Doing so builds up cute little towns as far as the eye can see!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126700/extras/93a99a5efea20f119662efc988acf3d0.poster.avif?t=1684485234\" width=192 height=108 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126700/extras/93a99a5efea20f119662efc988acf3d0.webm?t=1684485234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126700/extras/93a99a5efea20f119662efc988acf3d0.mp4?t=1684485234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126700/extras/bb4e583e2cb60903da79504758f01f68.poster.avif?t=1684485234\" width=192 height=108 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126700/extras/bb4e583e2cb60903da79504758f01f68.webm?t=1684485234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126700/extras/bb4e583e2cb60903da79504758f01f68.mp4?t=1684485234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126700/extras/9bb5f50198149c2134f0162ff99eb48b.poster.avif?t=1684485234\" width=192 height=108 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126700/extras/9bb5f50198149c2134f0162ff99eb48b.webm?t=1684485234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126700/extras/9bb5f50198149c2134f0162ff99eb48b.mp4?t=1684485234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Progression system</h2>The world starts out simple but soon you'll uncover more types of food, more kinds of animals and who knows what else?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Infinite procedural world</h2>The world of Double Trouble is carefully procedurally generated with different biomes to unlock and discover. No two game sessions are ever the same!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simple controls, stress-free gameplay</h2>Double Trouble is developed for (and tested by!) the youngest of gamers. Simple controls, colorful visuals and stress-free gameplay are sure to keep your little one engaged as they pick up a gamepad/keyboard for the first time!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126700/extras/645a76edc80755d57ed04a02fd1ee5ea.avif?t=1684485234\" width=576 height=64 /></span><br>Meet Olivia and Elodie, two sisters on an adventure in an infinite imaginary landscape. Can you help them work together in order to discover what secrets are in store?<br><br>Elodie is tasked with collecting food and luring out animals while Olivia guides animals to farms. Doing so builds up cute little towns as far as the eye can see!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126700/extras/93a99a5efea20f119662efc988acf3d0.poster.avif?t=1684485234\" width=192 height=108 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126700/extras/93a99a5efea20f119662efc988acf3d0.webm?t=1684485234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126700/extras/93a99a5efea20f119662efc988acf3d0.mp4?t=1684485234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126700/extras/bb4e583e2cb60903da79504758f01f68.poster.avif?t=1684485234\" width=192 height=108 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126700/extras/bb4e583e2cb60903da79504758f01f68.webm?t=1684485234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126700/extras/bb4e583e2cb60903da79504758f01f68.mp4?t=1684485234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126700/extras/9bb5f50198149c2134f0162ff99eb48b.poster.avif?t=1684485234\" width=192 height=108 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126700/extras/9bb5f50198149c2134f0162ff99eb48b.webm?t=1684485234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126700/extras/9bb5f50198149c2134f0162ff99eb48b.mp4?t=1684485234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Progression system</h2>The world starts out simple but soon you'll uncover more types of food, more kinds of animals and who knows what else?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Infinite procedural world</h2>The world of Double Trouble is carefully procedurally generated with different biomes to unlock and discover. No two game sessions are ever the same!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simple controls, stress-free gameplay</h2>Double Trouble is developed for (and tested by!) the youngest of gamers. Simple controls, colorful visuals and stress-free gameplay are sure to keep your little one engaged as they pick up a gamepad/keyboard for the first time!",
